title: Southee to captain NZ, McCullum rested PM's XI tour match
text: Southee to captain NZ, McCullum rested PM's XI tour match Wednesday, 21 October 2015 (1 minute ago) CANBERRA, Australia (AP) " New Zealand coach Mike Hesson says Tim Southee will captain the team in place of Brendan McCullum in Friday's opening Australian tour match against a Prime Minister's XI in Canberra.Hessan said Wednesday...
